<section class="W-SD">
  <h3>
    Overview of this Portrait Project
  </h3>
  <p>
    Throwback to 2016, I was the person in charge of all design related things in Safe Gold Financial Holdings.
    <br>
    <br>
    Once the renewal of the contract of Felix as the advertising person of the company was decided,
    we started preparing the plan of the contract renewal ceremony and arranging the photography.
    <br>
    <br>
    We analysed the designs for marketing in the past to find out what we wanted this time.
    After meeting with marketing and the advertising agency, the general direction of this photo shooting was settled - 4 themes: classic, formal, outdoor and sporty.
    <br>
    <br>
    On the day of contract renewal, the tailor was here to measure Felix.
    2 months of preparation, we met Felix again in a photographic studio.
  </p>
</section>

